title: Dan Siegel - Northern Nights (CBS ZK 44026)
description:
By David C. Filmer
This is a good collection. The title very song is good, along with "Love is the Power," "Falling Angel," and (to a lesser extent) "When it's Over." A couple of songs are not all that good, and the rest are OK.

BUT this album has Siegel's best-ever song, "Rhapsody." If you decide not to buy this album, at least browse over to "Along the Way" (Siegel's Greatest Hits collection) and spend a buck to download the track "Rhapsody." You won't be sorry
